# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok at this week 's summit of world leaders , the big winner will be the developing world , with the united states , europe and japan offering china , india , brazil and other emerging nations unprecedented new influence in global financial decisions .
# ::alignments
(w / win-01
      :ARG0 (w2 / world
            :ARG0-of (d / develop-02)
            :ARG1-of (m / mean-01
                  :ARG2 (o / offer-01
                        :ARG0 (a / and
                              :op1 (c / country
                                    :name (n / name
                                          :op1 "United"
                                          :op2 "States"))
                              :op2 (c2 / continent
                                    :name (n2 / name
                                          :op1 "Europe"))
                              :op3 (c3 / country
                                    :name (n3 / name
                                          :op1 "Japan")))
                        :ARG1 (a2 / and
                              :op1 (c4 / country
                                    :name (n4 / name
                                          :op1 "China"))
                              :op2 (c5 / country
                                    :name (n5 / name
                                          :op1 "India"))
                              :op3 (c6 / country
                                    :name (n6 / name
                                          :op1 "Brazil"))
                              :op4 (n7 / nation
                                    :ARG0-of (e / emerge-02)
                                    :mod (o2 / other)))
                        :ARG3 (ii / influence-01
                              :ARG0 a2
                              :ARG1 (d2 / decide-01
                                    :ARG3 (f / finance)
                                    :mod (g / globe))
                              :ARG1-of (n8 / new-01)
                              :mod (p / precedent
                                    :polarity -)))))
      :mod (b / big)
      :location (s / summit
            :mod (p2 / person
                  :ARG0-of (l / lead-02
                        :ARG1 (w3 / world)))
            :time (w4 / week
                  :mod (t / this))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok despite recent rumors that taiwan 's ruling kuomintang is dumping its overseas assets , a spokesman for a <unk> alaskan joint venture said the company has heard nothing about the issue and is operating normally .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (v / venture
                        :mod (j / joint)
                        :mod (c / country
                              :name (n / name
                                    :op1 "Alaskia")))
                  :ARG2 (s2 / spokesman)))
      :ARG1 (a / and
            :op1 (h2 / hear-01
                  :ARG0 v
                  :ARG1 (n2 / nothing
                        :topic (ii / issue-02)))
            :op2 (o / operate-01
                  :ARG0 v
                  :ARG1-of (n3 / normal-02)))
      :concession (r / rumor-01
            :ARG1 (d / dump-01
                  :ARG0 (g / government-organization
                        :name (n4 / name
                              :op1 "Kuomintang")
                        :ARG0-of (r2 / rule-03)
                        :poss (c2 / country
                              :name (n5 / name
                                    :op1 "Taiwan")))
                  :ARG1 (a2 / asset
                        :location (o2 / overseas)
                        :poss g))
            :time (r3 / recent)))

                  :weekday (f / friday)))

            :ARG0 (o / overcome-01
                  :ARG0 (n2 / news
                        :topic (c2 / company
                              :ARG0-of (e / earn-01)
                              :ARG1-of (s2 / solid-02)))
                  :ARG1 (c3 / concern-01
                        :ARG0 (h / hike-02
                              :ARG1 (r / rate
                                    :mod (ii / interest)))
                        :ARG1 (p / person
                              :ARG0-of (ii2 / invest-01)))
                  :ARG0-of (p2 / push-01
                        :ARG1 m2
                        :ARG2 (h2 / high-02
                              :ARG1 m2
                              :ARG2-of (h3 / have-degree-91
                                    :ARG1 m2
                                    :ARG3 (m3 / more
                                          :mod (m4 / modest))))))))

      :ARG0 (c / cowboy
            :mod (s / state
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Oklahoma")))
      :ARG1 (r / regain-01
            :ARG0 c
            :ARG1 (f / focus-01
                  :ARG1 c
                  :ARG2 (c2 / court
                        :mod (b / basketball))))
      :time (a / after
            :op1 (ii / interrupt-01
                  :ARG0 (t2 / tragedy)
                  :ARG1 (s2 / season
                        :poss c)
                  :manner (a2 / abrupt))))

                        :ARG1 (r / record)))

                        :ARG0 (t2 / team
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Toto"))
                        :ARG1 (t3 / team
                              :name (n4 / name
                                    :op1 "Guadalajara"))
                        :time (d / date-entity
                              :weekday (s2 / sunday)))))
      :op2 (m / maintain-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (l / lead-02
                  :ARG0 t2

                        :mod (s3 / soccer)
                        :time d
                        :season (w / winter))
                  :poss (c2 / country

                  :ord (o / ordinal-entity

(a / and
      :op1 (g / glided-01
            :ARG1 (a2 / and
                  :op1 (s / shuttle
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Space"
                              :op2 "Shuttle"))
                  :op2 (a3 / astronaut
                        :quant 6
                        :poss s))
            :destination (l / land-01
                  :ARG1 s
                  :ARG1-of (s2 / safe-01)
                  :manner (d / darkness))
            :time (d2 / date-entity
                  :weekday (t / thursday)
                  :dayperiod (e / early)))
      :op2 (e2 / end-01
            :ARG0 a2
            :ARG1 (m / mission-01
                  :ARG1 (s3 / station
                        :mod (ii / international)
                        :mod (s4 / space)
                        :poss-of (s5 / succeed-01
                              :ARG1-of (s6 / smooth-04)
                              :ARG1-of (u / upstage-01
                                    :ARG0 (d3 / drama
                                          :ARG1-of (h / high-02)
                                          :ARG1-of (c / cause-01
                                                :ARG0 (d4 / debris
                                                      :ARG1-of (f / float-01)
                                                      :mod (m2 / mystery)))))
                              :duration (b / brief))))))

                                    :op1 "The"
                                    :op2 "Student"
                                    :op3 "Room")))))
      :ARG4 (t / television)
      :manner (p3 / person
            :ARG0-of (p4 / produce-01
                  :ARG1 (s3 / series
                        :mod (r2 / reality
                              :mod (c / comic))
                        :location-of (t2 / try-01
                              :ARG0 (a / and
                                    :op1 (c2 / celebrity)

                                    :ARG2 c3))))))

(d / die-01
      :ARG1 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "thur"
                  :op2 "r."
                  :op3 "Kantrowitz")
            :mod (p2 / physicist)
            :ARG0-of (e / engineer-01)
            :ARG0-of (r / research-01
                  :ARG1 (b / behave-01
                        :ARG0 (a / and
                              :op1 (g / gas
                                    :mod (n2 / nucleus))
                              :op2 (d2 / dynamics
                                    :mod (f / fluid))))
                  :ARG0-of (l / lead-03
                        :ARG2 (a2 / and
                              :op1 (c / cone
                                    :mod (n3 / nose)
                                    :purpose (r2 / rocket))
                              :op2 (p3 / pump
                                    :mod n2)
                              :op3 (ii / idea
                                    :topic (f2 / fuse-01
                                          :mod n2
                                          :location (b2 / bottle
                                                :mod (m / magnet))))
                              :ARG1-of (ii2 / include-91
                                    :ARG2 (t / thing
                                          :mod (o / other)
                                          :quant (m2 / many)))))))
      :location (y / york
            :ARG1-of (n4 / new-01)
            :mod (g2 / government-organization
                  :name (n5 / name
                        :op1 "New"
                        :op2 "York"))))

                  :ARG0 a3

                        :ARG0 (t / troop
                              :poss a3)
                        :ARG1 (c / combat-01)
                        :location (c2 / country
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Afghanistan"))))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (s / saturday)))
      :op2 (c3 / convince-01
            :ARG0 a3
            :ARG1 (c4 / country
                  :name (n3 / name
                        :op1 "Russia"))

                  :ARG0 c4
